00:03:10.550 --> 00:03:14.300
it's a hundred. And this right over here is a
hundred higher than his initial balance.

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:17.470
So it makes sense that maybe he got the
profit out of an interest or

00:03:17.470 --> 00:03:18.239
something else

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:20.860
that he got in his bank account over the
first 30 days.

